-- China Erzhong to Raise as Much as 5.1 Billion Yuan in Private Placement
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-11-15T22:50:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/china-erzhong-to-raise-as-much-as-5-1-billion-yuan-in-private-placement.html
China Erzhong Group Deyang Heavy
Industries Co. plans to raise as much as 5.1 billion yuan ($767
million) via the private placement of as many as 400 million
shares, according to a statement to Shanghai’s stock exchange.  The company’s stock will resume trading today, according to
the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
